                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><persName role=\"author\">MYER S. ISAACS</persName>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">Attorney &amp; <sic>Counsellor</sic> at Law.</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">Notary Public,</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>243 BROADWAY, ROOMS 9 AND 10</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>Aug 27th 1868</date></p>\n            <p>My dear sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The receipt of your note and<lb/> enclosed communication\n                reminds<lb/> me that I had neglected acknowl<lb/>edging receipt of notice of meeting<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Josephi<add>?</add></persName> has gone to\n                    <placeName>Europe</placeName>, it is<lb/> quite out of my power, I regret\n                to<lb/> say to be with you on <date>Monday</date>. I<lb/> can't speak for\n                    <persName>Mr. Sa<add>?</add></persName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The article in the <hi rend=\"underline\">Israelite</hi> is<lb/>\n                scandalous — I had presumed an<lb/>\n                <add>?</add> reply which is in the<lb/> Messenger. Yours of course is too late<lb/>\n                this week (rec'd <date>Monday</date> at 10) but<lb/> it shall appear <hi\n                    rend=\"underline\">entire</hi>, I expect<lb/> next week with some remarks by<lb/>\n                a “trustee.” While I feel that<lb/> this contemptible assault is in the<lb/>\n                interest of men who fear their</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p30r9mw3j/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
