                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>“occupation will be gone” I <del>f</del><lb/> am as disgusted with our<lb/> orthodox\n                brethren who are very<lb/> slow to appreciate the necessity<lb/> of Hebrew\n                Education. You find<lb/> us of the <hi rend=\"underline\">Messenger</hi>\n                    working<add>?</add> pretty<lb/> steadily with the <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                    >Occident</hi> on this<lb/> question, but it is very, very<lb/>\n                <add>?</add> work to get <hi rend=\"underline\">money</hi> &amp;<lb/>\n                <hi rend=\"underline\">pupils</hi></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">You shall have 2 from <placeName>New York</placeName><lb/> (2\n                pupils) any others expected?<lb/> Please tell <persName>Mr Dropsie</persName> that\n                I<lb/> have <sic>despatched</sic> his notes to our<lb/> leading congregations,\n                with<lb/> more misgivings than hopes. We<lb/> must be unusually patient,<lb/> &amp;\n                persevere with the college<lb/> notwithstanding our limited</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p30r9mw3j/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
